    <item>
      <title>印度削减部分进口税以促进电子产品生产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/india-cuts-some-import-taxes-in-boost-for-electronics-production</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的政府寻求促进本土制造业的发展，因此在联邦预算中取消了多种电子元件的进口税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/india-cuts-some-import-taxes-in-boost-for-electronics-production</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 07:38:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度将放宽核法以吸引私人资本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/india-set-to-ease-nuclear-laws-to-draw-private-capital</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度财政部长尼尔玛拉·西塔拉曼表示，印度政府将修改核能法律，以吸引私人资本，促进该行业的发展，并依靠核能帮助该国摆脱对化石燃料的依赖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/india-set-to-ease-nuclear-laws-to-draw-private-capital</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 07:26:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>自英国脱欧公投以来，伦敦金融城受到的打击比其他地区更严重</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/city-of-london-hit-harder-than-rest-of-economy-since-brexit-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦金融城曾被视为英国主导服务业的明珠，但在英国脱欧公投后的几年里，其表现甚至比英国经济的其他领域还要差。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/city-of-london-hit-harder-than-rest-of-economy-since-brexit-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度明年将发行 1710 亿美元债券弥补赤字</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/india-to-sell-171-billion-bonds-next-year-to-fund-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度宣布下一财年将发行略高于预期的 14.82 万亿卢比（1,710 亿美元）债券，以弥补财政赤字。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/india-to-sell-171-billion-bonds-next-year-to-fund-spending</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 06:26:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
