    <item>
      <title>印度减税刺激支出，降低预算缺口目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/india-budget-targets-taxes-power-urban-areas-sitharaman-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度财政部长削减低收入者的税收，以刺激亚洲第三大经济体的消费，同时还计划在下一财年略微缩小预算赤字。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/india-budget-targets-taxes-power-urban-areas-sitharaman-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 06:12:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳门博彩收入低于预期，经济进一步放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/macau-gaming-revenue-misses-estimate-in-further-sign-of-slowdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳门 1 月份博彩收入下降 5.6%，低于分析师预期，进一步表明中国疲软的消费信心正在拖累这个世界最大博彩中心的复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/macau-gaming-revenue-misses-estimate-in-further-sign-of-slowdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 05:43:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾央行行长预计今年降息步伐将放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/philippine-central-banker-sees-slower-rate-cut-pace-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾央行行长埃利·雷莫洛纳表示，随着货币当局采取的政策宽松步伐放缓，今年基准利率可能下调半个百分点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/philippine-central-banker-sees-slower-rate-cut-pace-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 05:37:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税威胁迫在眉睫，韩国出口仍保持韧性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/south-korea-exports-stay-resilient-as-trump-tariff-threat-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国 1 月份出口保持增长势头，在年初因国内政治动荡和唐纳德·特朗普的关税威胁而蒙上阴影的情况下，保持了乐观情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/south-korea-exports-stay-resilient-as-trump-tariff-threat-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 00:14:30 GMT</pubDate>
